file.name: backend_security_openAPI.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Backend Security
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: 'http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html'
servers:
  - url: http://mockBackend:2383/v3
x-wso2-basePath: /backend-security
x-wso2-production-endpoints:
  urls:
    - http://mockBackend:2383/v2
  securityConfig:
    type: basic
    username: admin
    password: admin
  advanceEndpointConfig:
    circuitBreakers:
      maxConnections: 5
      maxRequests: 3
x-wso2-sandbox-endpoints:
  urls:
    - http://mockBackend:2390/v2
  securityConfig:
    type: basic
    username: guest
    password: password
paths:
  /echo:
    get:
      summary: Echo request
      operationId: echo
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Expected response to a valid request
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
components:
  schemas:
    Error:
      type: object
      required:
        - code
        - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
